\section{Conclusions}

The above considerations show that one can extend the applicability of the ideas of Ref. \cite{ZukStokes} to optical phenomena which are not polarization based, or related to pairs of spatially separated (multiport) interferometers \cite{MULTI}. The approach with rates leads to a clearer visibility of the Hong-Ou-Mandel effects, for higher pump values.


